SPECFEM2D/EXAMPLES/README_EXAMPLES

This directory contains a set of examples for testing purposes.

1. M2_UPPA     -- internal mesh with smooth topographic interfaces
2. fluid_solid -- external mesh, fluid, solid, and topography
3. Tromp2005   -- internal mesh, from Tromp, Tape, Liu (GJI 2005)
4. Tape2007    -- internal mesh, from Tape, Liu, Tromp (GJI 2007)

Each example requires a Par_file, SOURCE, and either a file of interfaces
OR an external mesh. The parameter files Par_file are written such that
the examples can be run in the current example directory, using the
processing script: ./process.sh

The default example is M2_UPPA. To setup a different example in the
main directory SPECFEM2D/, you must over-write the DATA/SOURCE and DATA/Par_file.
For example:
cp EXAMPLES/fluid_solid/Par_file_fluid_soild DATA/Par_file
cp EXAMPLES/fluid_solid/SOURCE_fluid_solid DATA/SOURCE
cp -r EXAMPLES/fluid_solid/mesh ./

The directory DATA_to_sort contains additional examples that have yet
to be sorted into folders as formal examples.

